  <summary date="2022-05-19T16:18:49Z" status="Introduced in House">Supporting Families of the Fallen Act

This bill increases from $400,000 to $500,000 the maximum coverage amount for members (or former members) of a uniformed service under the Servicemembers' Group Life Insurance program and the Veterans' Group Life Insurance program.</summary>
